David the tech says that HAARP and Fema are "trying to cause mass death"  
and "they are trying to cause an earth quake, but all they can do is create 
all  the massive rain"  David says, "God won't let them create an madrid  
quake"  at least i hope that's what i understood him to say.  "all  haarp is 
getting is the rain" they have been trying to play God,"  David  the t. says 
that if i tell you guys, "they won't believe it"  but, i got a  big mouth so 
i have to tell you to be careful, many people have loved ones that  got 
killed or hurt last night.  You guys know that what's going on in the  world is 
not the norm.  sure this may be spring and season for rain, but,  not at 
this level, somethings  a brew and it's not coffee.  sf
